headline: Jacobs to Optimize Data Centers with NVIDIA AI Factory Digital Twin Blueprint
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) to advance data centers via NVIDIA's Omniverse Blueprint for AI NVIDIA Omniverse Blueprint for AI factory digital twins – a blueprint to improve the design, simulation, deployment and operations of AI factories.
